OL,6,FBy Anna Geary
OL,8,FA charity has transcribed almost 100
OL,9,Fthousand pages from its vast archive
OL,10,Fof letters and records.
OL,12,FThomas Coram established the Foundling
OL,13,FHospital in 1739, as the UK's first
OL,14,Fhome for children whose parents were
OL,15,Funable to care for them.
OL,17,FAfter closing in 1954, it became the
OL,18,Fcharity, Coram, supporting young
OL,19,Fpeople and children.
