OL,6,FThe digital archive documents the
OL,7,Funtold stories of more than 20,000
OL,8,Fchildren who grew up at the hospital
OL,9,Fand of their birth mothers.
OL,11,FThe online archive has taken 5 years
OL,12,Fto collate involving nearly 6,500
OL,13,Fvolunteers from around the world.
