OL,6,FDr Carol Homden, CEO of Coram, said:
OL,7,FThrough these extensive and detailed
OL,8,Frecords, we are able to discover the
OL,9,Funtold stories of thousands of
OL,10,Fchildren who were raised at the
OL,11,FFoundling Hospital in the 18th and
OL,12,F19th centuries, and hear rare first-
OL,13,Fperson accounts of the issues faced by
OL,14,Fwomen who had no source of support in
OL,15,Fthe harsh environment before the
OL,16,Fwelfare state."
